              "items": [
                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3cf9js7m/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>may I call your attention to the resolution <add>?</add> I sent\n                                        you<lb/> by <persName>M Valentine</persName>, <add>?</add>\n                                        <persName>D<hi rend=\"sup\">r</hi>. E</persName> to lecture,\n                                        and the action of<lb/> the meeting <del>thereupon</del> on\n                                                  <persName>Lyons</persName> resignation, its\n                                        publication would<lb/> benefit our friend\n                                                  <persName>Eckman</persName> more especially as the\n                                        report<lb/> is current in <placeName>N Y.</placeName> that\n                                                  <persName>D<hi rend=\"sup\">r</hi>. E</persName> was\n                                        the cause of <persName>Lyons</persName> resig<lb/>nation,\n                                        the resolutions are public property and are officially<lb/>\n                                        sent to you. (the remarks of <persName>Valentine</persName>\n                                        you can omit if you<lb/> think proper. Merely state the\n                                        reason for <persName>Lyons</persName> resigning that<lb/>\n                                        the world may know the true cause. You also omitted<lb/> to\n                                        publish the <del>letter of</del> circular of the Members of\n                                        KKBE<lb/> (which I furnished you). Signed by a large number\n                                        of friends<lb/> of <persName>D<hi rend=\"sup\">r</hi>.\n                                                  E.</persName> approving his course on resigning)\n                                        the publication of this would<lb/> have done <persName>D<hi\n                                                  rend=\"sup\">r</hi>. E</persName> some permanent\n                                        good. I suppose you have<lb/> overlooked it. I have been\n                                        asked by very many of the<lb/>\n                                        <add>?</add> why you hesitated to publish it, <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">after promising me</hi><lb/>\n                                        <hi rend=\"underline\">that you would</hi>,</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I am highly delighted with your thoughts on the\n                                        Jewish<lb/> Ministry. I rejoice that you have come out <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">so boldly</hi><lb/> and denounced\n                                        the present mode of <hi rend=\"underline\">acting</hi> in\n                                        our<lb/> synagogue in your <hi rend=\"underline\">next</hi>\n                                        tell them something about praying<lb/> in the language they\n                                        understand, those who do not understand<lb/> the Hebrew and\n                                        make a believe they pray in it because they recite them\n                                        there prayers are of no use.<lb/> Advocate a portion of the\n                                        prayers to be read in English<lb/> viz <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                                                  >the <add>?</add></hi> and then afterwards in\n                                        Hebrew—and<lb/> the same with several others, so that the\n                                                  <hi rend=\"underline\">people</hi> may<lb/>\n                                        understand some of the service. Where lip service is an<lb/>\n                                        abomination, Now is the time to promulgate the<lb/> truth to\n                                        the people.</p>"
                  },
